net: dsa: mv88e6xxx: lock mutex in vlan_prepare

Lock the mutex in the mv88e6xxx_port_vlan_prepare function
called by the DSA stack, instead of doing it in the internal
mv88e6xxx_port_check_hw_vlan helper.

